Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:33.77,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.93,0:00:53.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:00.28,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.55,0:01:04.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:09.17,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:15.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:20.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:28.01,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:33.80,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.95,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:43.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:50.67,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想要獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第一榮譽的賽車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管生阿斯拉達隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在富士岡賽車場上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現了新開發的秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達GSX」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員是毫無賽車經驗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.55,0:02:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四歲少年 風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人雖然是第一次登場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他靈活運用了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電單車賽車的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的展現了高超的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一名通過了預賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F3的冠軍車手新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以其天才型的駕駛技術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如大家所預料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆的獲得壓倒性的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現了無比的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過幾個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就要變成戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在決戰的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要先聞一聞風的味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在決戰日的早上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是一大早就醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是葵車隊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經見識過「阿斯拉達GSX」了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是一部擁有無數優異性能的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過可惜的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的人選 卻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛的人選
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的能耐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看根本連「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之一的性能都無法發揮出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是好不容易才讓「阿斯拉達」上路的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜得對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…請你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 在今天的決賽裏觀眾就會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才車手新條直輝跟你這個平凡車手之間的差異了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話  富士岡錦標決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.23,0:04:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國的賽車迷們大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士岡選拔賽的決賽開賽時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正一分一秒接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢幻超科技的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭載著人工智慧導航系統的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑車大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將展現在大家眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富士岡選拔賽中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得前三名的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加全日本錦標賽的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場決賽可以說是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野心與夢想的白熱化戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跑道上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最被看好的賽車駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝已經出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 氣溫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,l8度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,48%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹 情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平．尾翼狀況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 「CYBER SYSTEM」狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們今天一定可以獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是憑我這個專業維修人員的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有預感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽開始前的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人坐立不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在場上的各輛賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經亮起了指示燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪些隊伍可以獲得參加全國錦標賽的資格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前三名的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底會落在哪一支隊伍的手中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張的氣氛越來越高漲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是富士岡的賽車場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.74,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不讓任何人有機會贏「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎麼樣 車田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我預料「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在隼人的駕駛之下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠跑完全程的機率只有7%而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7%
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼猜想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在最大離心力4.5G
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的一個半小時的車賽裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一個初賽者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑完全程是不太可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 在起跑線上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,24輛賽車已經排好位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這全長839．8公里繞場四十四圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長時間殘酷的戰爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾輛車子可以通過考驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠色旗子已經揮動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色信號燈亮起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綠燈亮起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先飛奔出來的是「SPERION」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在跑在最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑在最後面的是第24輛車「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是故障了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必著急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你升檔升得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓引擎轉動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 快降檔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」正在艱難奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也不能怪它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車手才十四歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是第一次正式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.22,0:08:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跑道上的垃圾一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人他比預賽的時候還差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太沒自信了 這個小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會甩尾 趕快回正方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 不要太專制了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們全體的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狹路到了 第四十圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」暫居第一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在進入第二圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「萊卡納」與「拉姆斯」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩輛車緊迫在後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太輕敵 新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會輸給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拉姆斯」跑到內圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼早就退場了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩輛車都進入直線道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色會變為幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最快的幻覺直線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:10:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想看到幻象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然跑出了時速423公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子的極速到底是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人跟得上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝選手一開賽就領先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負已經決定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下就只是不要被別人追上而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽如預期的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」暫居第一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入第九圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排在最後的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」與「史畢利」兩輛車子,完全被拋離了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要超過了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不是最後一輛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待機會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了 快上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以輸給那小鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行超車 危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過份了 怎麼可以這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他一點顏色瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達 還在混什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名的新條直輝選手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經超越阿斯拉達一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開 不要擋我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 別輸給他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝 你還在磨什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把這煩人的小鬼給解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我正在擺脫他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢了一圈的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」和「史畢利」以及「SPERION」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時偏離了車道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎發動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯拉達該不會是不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能優勝的新條直輝選手亦不能夠動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是也不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 快幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動輔助電力系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二秒鐘之後發動引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 快啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著打開一號選擇鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於,「阿斯拉達」復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞吞的在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不趕快走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 快進維修站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的是新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「萊卡納」躍居第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他車也陸陸續續的超過了「SPERION」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而阿斯拉達則進入了維修站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 讓你見識一下我高超的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」也進入了維修站
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子有點損傷,我看要花點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想因為這個事故而失去這場比賽的優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一名的阿斯拉達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經通過了底線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一下子新條的「SPERION」就變成最後一名了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備受矚目的新條直輝選手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能擺脫不利的狀況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然在拚命的往前衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」從後面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追趕上「阿斯拉達」了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有時間陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓你超過我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從「阿斯拉達」後面衝了上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒有辦法適應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高度的離心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」也毫不認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻加速中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在「阿斯拉達」與「SPERION」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們的時速都是445公里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二部車就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起朝著致命的600R前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身體去承受4.5G的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈橫向離心力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以說是致命的開法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「SPERION」的走道路線全記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在同樣的跑道上追上它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:15:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣必須要擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的體力和技術才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這麼做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就贏不了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 現在怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料已經輸入完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有辦法追上我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再堅持多會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣下去,該可以持續到終點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊迫新條直輝車子那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊跟在新條直輝選手車後面的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」的車手,風見隼人是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有十四歲的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於是代理車手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還沒有收到他的任何資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去收集他的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.71,0:17:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起衝向車陣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名次躍升到第十名之內了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽只剩下九圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四歲的風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現驚人的集中力以及持久力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條直輝選手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否能夠如預料中一般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像失去知覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過了這麼激烈的離心力挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「SPERION」終於追上了「萊卡納」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是「萊卡納」也毫不是讓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢,「拉巴姆」因為機件故障被迫離場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.06,0:18:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就升上第五名了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面這兩輛如果能超越
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能超過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是第三名了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊!終點指示燈已經亮起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超不過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時四十分鐘的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於進入了最高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的高速彎道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致命的600R
